<h4><a href="https://www.theverge.com/2020/9/17/21444506/apple-ios-14-2-beta-shazam-identify-music-phone-apps-headphones">iOS 将支持应用内曲目识别</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1366699" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Shazam_Control_Center.jpg" alt="" width="920" height="568" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Shazam_Control_Center.jpg 920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Shazam_Control_Center-360x222.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Shazam_Control_Center-768x474.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 920px) 100vw, 920px" /></p>
<p>The Verge 消息，在 iOS 14.2 开发者预览版中，用户将可直接识别手机应用中在播放的音乐，相关功能按钮就控制中心里。2018 年，苹果收购音乐识别应用 Shazam，现在看来开始更多地将该应用功能结合到系统原生功能中。</p>
<p>此前，用户已可通过 Siri 来识别扬声器可接收到的外放音乐，但新功能让用户戴着耳机看视频或听歌时，也能随时辨别出曲目。</p>
<h4><a href="https://hypebeast.cn/2020/9/gopro-hero-9-black-action-camera-release">GoPro 发布 Hero 9 Black</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1366700" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/gopro-hero-9-black-action-camera-release-004.jpg" alt="" width="1400" height="933" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/gopro-hero-9-black-action-camera-release-004.jpg 1400w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/gopro-hero-9-black-action-camera-release-004-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/gopro-hero-9-black-action-camera-release-004-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/gopro-hero-9-black-action-camera-release-004-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px" /></p>
<p>Hypebeast 消息，GoPro 发布 Hero 9 Black，采用了彩色前置屏幕，为用户带来除了其背面的触控屏幕之外的第二个显示屏幕，国行预售价为 3498 元。</p>
<p>性能方面，GoPro Hero 9 Black 的电池续航时间延长了 30%、防水能力到达 33 英尺，可拍摄 20MP 静止图像以及录制 5K 影片，具有超广角的可拆卸镜头选件。</p>
